ffectual by the acknowledging of every good thing which is in you in Christ Jesus.","year":64},{"id":"recLjsx1bVfcKLkvb","ref":"Phlm.1.7","text":"For we have great joy and consolation in thy love, because the bowels of the saints are refreshed by thee, brother.","year":64},{"id":"recEPyRHPQyI1mrDs","ref":"Phlm.1.8","text":"Wherefore, though I might be much bold in Christ to enjoin thee that which is convenient,","year":64}]}
